http://www.asc.nasa.gov/ascsite/ASCGoalObj.htm

    Goals and Objectives:



   Goal:

     Safely enable major increases in the capacity and productivity of
     the National Airspace System through development of revolutionary
     operations systems and vehicle concepts

     [ASC_NAS.PSD.gif]

    Objectives:
     * Improve capacity, efficiency and access of the National Airspace
       System
     * Increase collaboration, predictability and flexibility for the NAS
       users
     * Develop advanced vehicle concepts and technologies for
       runway-independent operations
     * Maintain safety and minimize environmental effects
     * Develop, validate and transfer these advanced concepts,
       technologies and procedures to the customer community
